{"tid":463520,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【唔使傷心】嘉倩BB以外 新一代新聞小花","createTime":"2017-11-09T14:31:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-10T13:56:20.000Z","uid":29675,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"7161bbae8b5c6ef1090b1344819ac38bb981f547","tid":463520,"uid":29675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T14:31:22.000Z","msg":"一講開新聞小花，第一個會諗起嘅，應該係TVB樣靚聲甜主播陳嘉倩。可惜嘉倩BB早前離開大台，返去校園做全職學生，唔少觀眾都覺得可惜。最近有網友介紹幾位新聞小花，外型氣質都拍得住嘉倩BB，而且各有特色，梗有一個啱你心水。<br />\n<br />\n左文薏<br />\n<img src=\"https://78.media.tumblr.com/d42d0d33c8640b9636d3e5c47e9379bc/tumblr_inline_oz5323Ursq1u03abq_1280.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F78.media.tumblr.com%2Fd42d0d33c8640b9636d3e5c47e9379bc%2Ftumblr_inline_oz5323Ursq1u03abq_1280.jpg&h=751940c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n左文薏於2016年加入now新聞及財經台做實習記者，佢個樣比較可愛，把聲又甜到漏，成功吸引觀眾朝早睇新聞。有網民話每朝要睇完佢報新聞先返工。<br />\n<br />\n丘靜雯<br />\n<img src=\"https://78.media.tumblr.com/f2d82cfd96e186eee633590ec47a1d64/tumblr_inline_oz5372Uyec1u03abq_1280.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F78.media.tumblr.com%2Ff2d82cfd96e186eee633590ec47a1d64%2Ftumblr_inline_oz5372Uyec1u03abq_1280.jpg&h=56acf04a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n丘靜雯（Nicole）係Now的嘅新聞主播，通常係深宵新聞時段出現，因貌似韓國女子組合Apink隊長初瓏，所以吸引到一班網民留意。佢幕前報新聞個樣比較正經同cool，但見佢個人ig都上載唔少扮鬼臉嘅相，估計佢私底下都幾玩得。<br />\n<br />\n梁凱寧<br />\n<img src=\"https://78.media.tumblr.com/c258c68fd1b77f52d1ae974b15c500ed/tumblr_inline_oz52slKlJt1u03abq_1280.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F78.media.tumblr.com%2Fc258c68fd1b77f52d1ae974b15c500ed%2Ftumblr_inline_oz52slKlJt1u03abq_1280.jpg&h=070104f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n梁凱寧（Maggie）大學二年級暑假時已經喺無綫新聞部實習，由於佢樣貌甜美、身材出眾而被網民留意。有網民留意到佢身材，話好令人好分心。<br />\n<br />\n羅鈺文<br />\n<img src=\"https://78.media.tumblr.com/f6ffee45cad93d6bad1076374e1d4856/tumblr_inline_oz52vmxRO71u03abq_1280.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F78.media.tumblr.com%2Ff6ffee45cad93d6bad1076374e1d4856%2Ftumblr_inline_oz52vmxRO71u03abq_1280.jpg&h=94e250db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n羅鈺文（Yuki）靚女斯文，笑起上來好可愛，仲吸引到一班男網民將佢報導天氣嘅片段剪輯。羅鈺文畢業於香港理工大學護理系，亦係一名註冊護士。但佢無去醫護界發展，竟然選擇跑新聞。佢之前喺亞視新聞部任記者及主播，之後離職去修讀香港中文大學新聞系碩士課程，2012年加入無綫成為主播。<br />\n<br />\n賴凱靖<br />\n<img src=\"https://78.media.tumblr.com/d127b8ee2e6a02b71ba4b6849d9dfbdd/tumblr_inline_oz52u7cykt1u03abq_1280.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F78.media.tumblr.com%2Fd127b8ee2e6a02b71ba4b6849d9dfbdd%2Ftumblr_inline_oz52u7cykt1u03abq_1280.jpg&h=c78c6489&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n賴凱靖2017年加入無線新聞台，外形比起幾位同期女主播甜美，有網民覺得佢可以做陳嘉倩接班人。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n無提藍可盈,陳詠賢,陳海雯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30e49562059f93a60d8c2333074e96a97c41fe38","tid":463520,"uid":28195,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T14:52:01.000Z","msg":"仆你個街，無金盈既？"},{"pid":"5e7b5dad5413374bd4007bf08a33382804d48901","tid":463520,"uid":54516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T12:36:42.000Z","msg":"仆你個街，乜淨係得CCTVB有女主播咩？而且CCTVB而家主播同記者樣貌真係愈來愈差。<br />\n成日講新聞女郎，男呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7d36191c675c3f06a72d11d2c2ec587d2e98d35","tid":463520,"uid":136252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T13:50:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>仆你個街，無金盈既？</blockquote><br />\nCHING識貨"},{"pid":"9c0b09925827ab8aa673841f9c9c7b69bd04b8e9","tid":463520,"uid":111814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T13:56:20.000Z","msg":"羅鈺文都新一代小花<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}